-- Argentina’s Hipotecario to Distribute 5% Stake Among Employees
-- B y   P a b l o   G o n z a l e z
-- 2012-11-13T11:38:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-13/argentina-s-hipotecario-to-distribute-5-stake-among-employees.html
Argentina ’s  Banco Hipotecario SA (BHIP) ,
the country’s biggest mortgage lender, will grant a 5 percent
stake to employees through a shared ownership program, the
official gazette said today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
